      • SettingsPanel

        private SettingsPanel()
        The constructor for SettingsPanel. Creates a new GridBagLayout and adds all JLabels and JFormattedTextFields. All fields are configured to only accept integer inputs. Adds a PropertyChangeListener to all fields that listens to changes to the value property.

    • Method Detail

      • propertyChange

        public void propertyChange​(java.beans.PropertyChangeEvent evt)
        Invoked whenever a bound property is changed. Stores the value of each field. The number of rows and the length of each row is then determined as follows:
        • The number of Tables is divided evenly into the number of rows.
        • All leftover tables are added one at a time to a row starting from the first row.
        Based on all inputed values the Students are rearranged into tables and all table sizes and positions are calculated.
        Specified by:
        propertyChange in interface java.beans.PropertyChangeListener
